{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Selected by the fickle finger of fate, Abe\u2122, floor-waxer first class for RuptureFarms, was catapulted into a life of adventure when he overheard plans by his boss, Molluck the Glukkon\u2122, to turn Abe and his fellow Mudokons into Tasty Treats as part of a last-ditch effort to rescue Molluck's failing meat-packing empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\t\t\t\t\t                        During his escape from RuptureFarms, Abe received a vision from the mysterious Big Face, showing Abe that he must not only rescue his fellow Mudokons, but also protect all of Oddworld's creatures from the predatory Magog Cartel.                                                 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\t\t\t\t\t                        After completing arduous Temple trials, and journeying across a wasteland with his friend Elum, Abe was granted the awesome power of the Shrykull. Returning to RuptureFarms, Abe destroyed the foul slaughterhouse, rescued his buddies, and brought down some righteous lightning on top of Molluck's pointy head.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/15700/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728644292","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/15700/page.bg.jpg?t=1728644292","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/15700/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728644292","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/15700/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728644292","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Trading Cards","id":29},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":15730,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Selected by the fickle finger of fate, Abe\u2122, floor-waxer first class for RuptureFarms, was cata